{"tid":2455703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林門鄭氏：很有信心香港在中共全力支持下再創癲峰","createTime":"2021-03-21T10:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T10:57:48.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"830fde342ea93105a3e731ad9d05e88c0e2b81e9","tid":2455703,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:29:28.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥日前表示，很有信心香港在中央全力支持下會繁榮興旺，再創高峰。<br />\n<br />\n　　20日晚，中國發展高層論壇2021年會香港專場以視頻形式舉行，主題為&ldquo;香港未來五年的發展&rdquo;。林鄭月娥在會上發言時作上述表示。<br />\n<br />\n　　林鄭月娥說，她對香港和香港未來發展的信心，是基於全國人大所作出的兩項重大決定，即2020年6月關於香港特區維護國家安全立法的決定，以及為落實&ldquo;愛國者治港&rdquo;原則於近期通過的關於完善香港特區選舉制度的決定。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://www.hkcna. hk/content/2021/0321/886439.shtml</code></pre>"},{"pid":"d98dda5b5cc54c6d8e18618cb791bc059483ac9b","tid":2455703,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"連匪安法都立得. 點會唔可以進入另一個 癲峰丫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f91dec86e70a7f084805ca5cff3671a5c0c7ab","tid":2455703,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:49:48.000Z","msg":"有七婆呢句我好安心，黎緊應該仆街"},{"pid":"782968677f6448b09d6b1dcb27cf5370a31067fa","tid":2455703,"uid":206003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:56:03.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong is ended"},{"pid":"ed24b9d1a5d9b0b69f23584cc6f1f39115ca3341","tid":2455703,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:57:02.000Z","msg":"咁香港加速玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bec717d34e39545baad514b754e27d34d580b9c","tid":2455703,"uid":30274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:57:48.000Z","msg":"再創瘋癲就有份"}]}